---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Martial Arts School Marketing in Canada | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/fitness-gyms/martial-arts" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Martial Arts
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Martial Arts</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">12 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Martial Arts School Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
          Convert trials, retain families, and build students who earn black belts with automated sequences.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Martial arts schools build character and discipline, but most struggle with retention. Students start excited and quit after a few belts. Automation that nurtures families through the journey changes everything.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Trial Conversion</h2>

          <p>
            That first trial class creates excitement, but without follow-up, families don't enroll. Sequences that address concerns, offer incentives, and create urgency convert trials into memberships.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Belt Progression</h2>

          <p>
            Students who feel progress stay. Automated reminders for belt tests, preparation tips, and celebrations keep students motivated through each rank advancement.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-4">Family Expansion</h2>

          <p>
            When one child trains, siblings and parents often sit idle. Campaigns that offer family trials, sibling discounts, and adult classes expand revenue per family significantly.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-red-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your School?</h3>
            <p class="text-amber-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd implement these automations for your martial arts school.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-amber-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
